ActNational Energy Board Act
National Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-317 - GNL Québec Inc.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-317 to GNL Québec Inc. to export gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of the natural gas liquefaction facility to be located at the port of Saguenay, also called the port of Grande-Anse in La Baie, Québec.
